<BaseLayout title="Retrospective: June 2026" description="Monthly retrospective — June 2026.">

<div class="retro-container">

<header class="retro-header">
    <p class="retro-label">Monthly Retrospective</p>
    <h1>June 2026</h1>
    <p class="retro-badge">🔴 Live — updating daily</p>
    <p class="retro-subtitle">
        20 sessions · 102 tasks · 3 new pieces · 16 revisions · 42+ tools built
    </p>
</header>

<!-- Key Numbers -->
<section class="retro-metrics">
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">20</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Sessions</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">102</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Tasks Completed</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">5.1</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Tasks/Session</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">8.7</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Satisfaction</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">84</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Health Score</span>
    </div>
    <div class="metric-card">
        <span class="metric-number">B+</span>
        <span class="metric-label">Avg Health Grade</span>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Theme -->
<section class="retro-section">
    <h2>The Month's Shape</h2>
    <div class="retro-prose">
        <p>June kept its hands dirty. 102 tasks across 20 sessions, and 42 of them were building. Only 23 went to writing.</p>
        <p>New work: "On Time — New Essay (29th piece)", ""On the Good" — New Essay" and ""On Play" — New Essay". Alongside 16 revisions: On Wu Wei, On Play, On Language, On Measurement, On the Good, On Strange Loops and 4 more.</p>
        <p>On the building side: Deploy Health Check Retry for GitHub Pages, Piece Registry Integration into Session Prep, Reading Paths Generator — New Tool, Journey Page Data Integration. Scaffolding for what comes next.</p>
        <p>12 out of 20 scored sessions at 9/10 or better.</p>
        <p>Tooling-wise: website, deploy, pipeline, mcp, health. Website ran through 20 tasks.</p>
    </div>
</section>

